Healer- (5)
- During the night, the Healer can tend to a respawning players wounds, speeding up their respawn progress by 2 phases.
- Cannot target players who are not respawning.
- The target affected will be informed. Respawn times cannot be reduced beyond 1 phase.
- Healing is a post-night action. 2 phase cooldown.
- Respawns in 4 phases.
